  "question_id": "71b9253b-3ef6-4570-ac88-781cbf49a424",
  "short_text": "Hollow Right Angled Triangle - 6",
  "content": "Given a number `N`, write a program to print the **Hollow Inverted Right Angled Triangle** of `N` rows using stars (`*`).\r\n\r\n```\r\n* * * * *\r\n  *     *\r\n    *   *\r\n      * *\r\n        *\r\n```\r\n\r\n<MultiLineNote>\r\nThere is a space after every star (`*`).\r\n</MultiLineNote>\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n####Input\r\n\r\nThe input will be a single line containing an integer representing `N`.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n####Output\r\n\r\nThe output should be `N` rows containing stars (`*`) as the **Hollow Inverted Right Angled Triangle** shown in the sample output.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n#### Explanation\r\n\r\nFor example, if the given number is `N = 4`,\r\n\r\n- Print the stars (`*`) on **4** rows as shown in the given image.\r\n\r\n<Img imageSrc='https://assets.ccbp.in/frontend/content/programming-foundations/cx-hollow-right-angled-triangle-6.png' widthPercent='70'/>\r\n\r\n<MultiLineNote>\r\n\r\nIn the given image,\r\n\r\n- The Empty box indicates two spaces (\"&nbsp;&nbsp;\").\r\n- The Star in the box indicates the star and a space (\"\\* \").\r\n\r\n</MultiLineNote>\r\n\r\nThe output should be,\r\n\r\n```\r\n* * * *\r\n  *   *\r\n    * *\r\n      *\r\n\r\n```",
  "question_type": "CODING",
  "content_type": "MARKDOWN",
  "codes": [
    {
      "code_id": "21d16eca-cccf-453d-aab2-f28b72af3b61",
      "code_content": "n = int(input())\n\nfirst_row = \"* \" * n\nprint(first_row)\n\nfor i in range(1, n-1):\n    left_spaces = \" \" * 2 * i\n    middle_spaces = \" \" * (2 * (n - i) - 3)\n    row = left_spaces + \"*\" + middle_spaces + \"*\"\n    print(row)\n    \nleft_spaces = \" \" * 2 * (n - 1)\nlast_row = left_spaces + \"*\"\nprint(last_row)",
      "language": "PYTHON",
      "default_code": true
    }
  ],
